Title: An action for supergravity interacting with super-p-brane sources
Authors: Igor A. Bandos, Jose A. de Azcarraga, Jose M. Izquierdo and Jerzy
  Lukierski
Comments: One short clarifying comment added. To appear in PRD (Rapid Commun.)
Report-no: FTUV/01-2404, IFIC/01-22, April 24, 2001
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D65 (2002) 021901
\\
  We describe the coupled system of supergravity and a superbrane source by the
sum of the group manifold action for D--dimensional supergravity and the action
for a super--$p$--brane. We derive the generalized Einstein equation with the
source and discuss the local fermionic symmetries of the coupled action. Our
scheme could be especially relevant in $D=11, 10$, in which the superfield
actions for supergravity are not known.
